<p>+1 from me.</p>
<p>The ConProcs and ACS fits this anomaly perfectly. The description is probably a bit lacking but then again, its a modern day brothel run by Incubi so I get why it would be lacking in description. The real good thing I enjoyed from all of this was the Addendum, with the interviews.</p>
<p>I did love the fact that Adams was in serious trouble because of him being a pervert. I also love how they are some genuine demons who haven't tried to break the Veil, just trying to get through life. Although the Incident Log flew over my head but I'm guessing it was significant in another story.</p>
<p>TLDR: You did good humour, it fits in nicely with how I would have imagined an underVegas would look like, and it feels nice to read a business skip not breaking the Veil. +1</p>

